List of components
------------------

- NanoPi NEO Air
- SD Card (>= 128 GB)
- BMP180: air pressure and temperature sensor (i2c)
- PCF8591: a/d converter (i2c) for monitoring battery status
- SSD1306: display (i2c)
- ULN2803: darlington transistor array, used as status LED driver


- Push buttons (for switching camera on/off)
- Adafruit Ultimate GPS Breakout - 66 channel w/10 Hz updates - Version 3
- Active GPS antenna with SMA connector
- Battery box for six AA akkus
- M8 threaded bar + screw nuts + butterfly nuts
- Mini360 DC-DC Buck Converter Step Down Module 



